      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 15:53:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国将从贷款机构购买退伍军人错过的抵押贷款，以阻止丧失抵押品赎回权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-16/us-will-buy-veterans-mortgage-arrears-to-halt-home-foreclosures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据退伍军人事务部的最新指导，美国再次从贷款人那里购买拖欠的抵押贷款，重新启动了一种流行的解决方案，以防止拥有房屋的退伍军人丧失抵押品赎回权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-16/us-will-buy-veterans-mortgage-arrears-to-halt-home-foreclosures</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 15:41:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
