      <title>1 月份美国消费者信心指数升至 79.6</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-16/us-consumer-sentiment-increases-to-79-6-in-january-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2 月份美国消费者信心指数连续第三个月有所改善，信心指数微升 0.6 点至 79.6，为 2021 年 7 月以来的最高水平。迈克尔·麦基 (Michael McKee) 在彭博电视台报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-16/us-consumer-sentiment-increases-to-79-6-in-january-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 15:40:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储巴尔表示监管机构正在关注商业房地产风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-16/fed-s-barr-says-regulators-eyeing-cre-risk-downgrade-more-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储首席银行监管机构表示，美国监管机构“密切关注”商业房地产贷款的风险，并在其财务面临新压力的情况下加大了对贷款机构监管评级的下调力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-16/fed-s-barr-says-regulators-eyeing-cre-risk-downgrade-more-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 14:10:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
